title: How Psychedelics Changed My Life
itunes:title: How Psychedelics Changed My Life
description:
I would be a complete hypocrite if I did not tell you about the largest strides that I have made in my person development. Those massive strides came from the use of psychedelics in a ceremonial format. All I ask, is that you listen to this episode with an open mind. I am not trying to sell you on doing any of what I talk about, I just want to open your mind to what I have been doing the past two years.

If you want to learn more about Rythmia and ayahuasca here is the link https://robdial.com/rythmia

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
